ANNE,What?
ABIGAIL,It is gone. I did not know who’s attention to bring it to. Shall I request it back on his return? Quietly perhaps?
ANNE,You are saying Sarah diverted money to him?
ANNE,It does seem so. Some seven thousand.
ABIGAIL,She would not.
